Are you done?

830
00:41:00.500 --> 00:41:02.169
I'm so full.

831
00:41:05.714 --> 00:41:07.339
Your mom is so cool.

832
00:41:07.340 --> 00:41:09.175
She doesn't even look like a mom.

833
00:41:09.176 --> 00:41:10.759
That's just because she's so young.

834
00:41:10.760 --> 00:41:12.261
How old is she. anyways?

835
00:41:12.262 --> 00:41:14.430
Like... 35.

836
00:41:14.431 --> 00:41:16.390
Mm. Still kind of old.

837
00:41:16.391 --> 00:41:18.309
Just not as old as my parents.

838
00:41:18.310 --> 00:41:19.977
So...

839
00:41:19.978 --> 00:41:21.812
where's your dad?

840
00:41:21.813 --> 00:41:23.981
Does he. like. live somewhere else. or...

841
00:41:23.982 --> 00:41:27.026
No. uh... He's dead.

842
00:41:27.027 --> 00:41:29.820
I've never met anyone
with a dead dad before.

843
00:41:29.821 --> 00:41:33.657
Well. I guess now you have.

844
00:41:33.658 --> 00:41:37.620
Sometimes things just come
out of my mouth. That was really...

845
00:41:37.621 --> 00:41:38.871
weird and...

846
00:41:38.872 --> 00:41:40.916
