847
00:41:41.791 --> 00:41:43.167
I'm sorry about your dad.

848
00:41:43.168 --> 00:41:44.293
Thanks.

849
00:41:44.294 --> 00:41:46.378
And I'm sorry for bringing him up.
I d-- I didn't know.

850
00:41:46.379 --> 00:41:48.255
Ooh. no. I'm glad.

851
