<i>♪ Ooh. ooh-ooh-ooh ♪</i>

903
00:44:54.192 --> 00:44:57.319
<i>♪ Ooh-ooh-ooh. ooh-ooh-ooh ♪</i>

904
00:44:57.320 --> 00:45:01.199
