948
00:48:44.088 --> 00:48:47.215
<i>♪ Da. da-da. da-da. da...</i>

949
00:48:47.216 --> 00:48:49.177
Percy.
this is my girlfriend. Taylor.

950
00:48:50.178 --> 00:48:51.970
<i>♪ Da. da-da ♪</i>

951
00:48:51.971 --> 00:48:54.139
<i>♪ da-da-da-da...</i>

952
00:48:54.140 --> 00:48:55.223
Hi.

953
00:48:55.224 --> 00:48:57.225
Hey. It's really nice to meet you.

954
00:48:57.226 --> 00:48:58.353
Same.

955
00:48:59.854 --> 00:49:02.606
♪ ♪

956
00:49:02.607 --> 00:49:03.690
Let me help with your bags.

957
00:49:03.691 --> 00:49:05.442
Yeah.

958
00:49:06.944 --> 00:49:11.949
<i>♪ No fair ♪</i>

959
00:49:17.914 --> 00:49:20.332
<i>I was so anxious</i>

960
00:49:20.333 --> 00:49:21.625
<i>to see him again.</i>

961
00:49:21.626 --> 00:49:25.337
<i>I really thought that I just had
to get through that.</i>

962
00:49:28.800 --> 00:49:30.175
It's been a long time. Percy.

963
00:49:30.176 --> 00:49:32.094
<i>A lot's happened.</i>

964
00:49:32.095 --> 00:49:33.428
So how are you holding up?

965
00:49:36.599 --> 00:49:39.059
I think it's really great
that you came back here.

966
00:49:39.060 --> 00:49:40.645
but you have missed. like. a lot.

967
00:49:43.106 --> 00:49:44.356
<i>Why would she go back there?</i>

968
00:49:44.357 --> 00:49:46.149
After everything they put her through?

969
00:49:47.902 --> 00:49:49.653
If he found out what I did...

970
00:49:49.654 --> 00:49:50.863
You have to stop punishing yourself.

971
00:49:51.864 --> 00:49:54.533
Percy being here is bad for me.

972
00:49:56.411 --> 00:49:58.328
<i>When I'm with her. I don't think.</i>

973
00:49:58.329 --> 00:49:59.956
<i>At all.</i>

974
00:50:01.165 --> 00:50:03.208
Seeing you guys together
felt like a scene out of the past.

975
00:50:03.209 --> 00:50:05.419
Percy and I were over a long time ago.

976
00:50:05.420 --> 00:50:06.587
<i>I'm with Taylor now.</i>

977
00:50:07.422 --> 00:50:09.089
I never know where I stand with you.

978
00:50:09.090 --> 00:50:10.758
You want me and then you don't.

979
00:50:12.135 --> 00:50:13.594
<i>It's confusing and hurtful.</i>

980
00:50:18.349 --> 00:50:20.142
If Sam knew why you left...

981
00:50:20.143 --> 00:50:21.936
Sam can never. ever know.

982
00:50:22.812 --> 00:50:23.812
Ah!

983
00:50:23.813 --> 00:50:27.441
<i>How you might only have
one chance at happiness...</i>

984
00:50:28.860 --> 00:50:30.152
Come on. you got this!

985
00:50:32.280 --> 00:50:33.363
<i>...at love.</i>

986
00:50:33.364 --> 00:50:34.698
But what if you don't?

987
00:50:38.411 --> 00:50:39.661
<i>Sam...</i>

988
00:50:39.662 --> 00:50:42.122
there's something I have to tell you.

989
00:50:42.123 --> 00:50:44.750
♪ ♪

990
00:50:44.751 --> 00:50:46.794
<i>♪ Is yours ♪</i>

